{{Otheruses|Imperial Justice}}
{{Quote|By Imperial law, when the Emperor takes a wife, she becomes his property, obliged to obey his every word and bow down before him whenever he wishes a show of obedience.|Bertroff Hissa, reading from the ''Dark Book of Imperial Justice''|<ref name="Queen of the Empire">''[[Queen of the Empire]]''</ref>}}
The '''''Dark Book of Imperial Justice''''' contained a passage involving [[Trioculus' Empire|Imperial]] wedding regulations. [[Bertroff Hissa]] read from it at the wedding of [[Trioculus]] and a [[Leia Organa II|Leia Organa]] [[Human replica droid]].

